flowchart TD
    A[Go File Edit] --> B[gofmt + goimports]
    B --> C[go vet ./...]
    C --> D{vet clean?}
    D -- No --> E[Block: GO-VET-001]
    D -- Yes --> F[golangci-lint run]
    F --> G{Lint clean?}
    G -- No --> E
    G -- Yes --> H[go test -race ./...]
    H --> I{Tests pass?}
    I -- No --> E
    I -- Yes --> J[Merge]
